<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Yep Hero Hall bar none, Only pacify till you get it down pat then just pull two at once, pull with tash then root first one sick pet on other while your back peddling. Other agroed mob will stick fast to pet. This will save you mana as pacify is like 350 or something and tash and fetter only 170 I think. Plus first mob almost always goes down faster then fetter wears off. This place is almost perfect for a charming chanter after those extra two mobs were added at the back. You should be able to clear all 16 just around the time of when repops start happening. I always try to keep both heros at front cleared as soon as they pop. So you can pull named as they path by. Great place to gm baking also you'll have more meats then you know what to do with after awhile, plus makes a good stat food that moves fast in bazaar. When pet is low on health break and root it then grab anouther pet to kill at a 4k mana pool don't waste mana on nukes, Take the xp hit on ex pet and just go for non stop killing even at 4k you should be able to keep going till your eyes are bleeding.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
